The paper proposes a method for improving the quality evaluation of Wikipedia medical articles using Natural Language Processing (NLP) and dictionaries-based techniques. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Cybernetics (cs.CY).
